{"tid":1614762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非割 但搞藍店唔應該一視同仁","createTime":"2019-10-03T01:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T06:20:51.000Z","uid":217729,"like":52,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"794fb61e882b3f934c0dbeae002dccb29c49913f","tid":1614762,"uid":217729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:33:17.000Z","msg":"正如成日鬧警察用咗過份武力，我地都應該用最低武力。<br />\n<br />\n福建幫、圍村佬，打咁多人係應該繼續破壞，尤其是麻雀館，第一個感覺已經係三教九流，打爛晒都冇人會同情(唔好燒鋪) <br />\n<br />\n但美心太子女始於冇傷人，美心都同佢割席，佢又唔係大股東。個人覺得唔應該一視同仁，用最低武力的話，似乎應該低一個level，例如噴字、封佢門口//齋坐？<br />\n<br />\n吉野家我覺得應該再低一個層次，罷食，甚至齋坐就好。"},{"pid":"133e819688da86255a6b877f049ac3d00bcb39b0","tid":1614762,"uid":217729,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:34:48.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"11f7caaa0aa0c98da45bbfed9c5dafbe60fbbe6d","tid":1614762,"uid":217729,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:35:07.000Z","msg":"非割席"},{"pid":"f54ad35b2b62df150ba52fb29922da862c8d454e","tid":1614762,"uid":148980,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:35:16.000Z","msg":"有得諗"},{"pid":"cae6deb28f577636370250bc0addcd4c742c3129","tid":1614762,"uid":99391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:36:03.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"1f6cc90c43516422a72cc592b5e7ec92c540157e","tid":1614762,"uid":217729,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:36:40.000Z","msg":"非帶風向..."},{"pid":"080686c5a1dcd04325e043eee1d592ea7e1c09ce","tid":1614762,"uid":299164,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:38:31.000Z","msg":"針對性，針對性打擊<br />\n打擊中資，奶共商家佬<br />\n打破壟斷，支持小店<br />\n振興裝修業<br />\n目標清晰"},{"pid":"4e198ece888c937d440e576696c6cea7d35f36d7","tid":1614762,"uid":82655,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:38:38.000Z","msg":"雖然唔太認同，但照推<br />\n一齊討論"},{"pid":"9af67605536004781d2527f30a627be7032358c8","tid":1614762,"uid":997,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score"